sentences: Sophie Luise Elisabeth Muller (born 31 January 1962) is a British music video director from London, who has produced more than 300 music videos.
She won a Grammy Award for Annie Lennox's 1992 Diva video album, and an MTV Video Music Award for Lennox's song "Why" from the same album.
